defaultGeneral Remarksdefault&#xa0;default4.
default The NFRN understands the importance of the
default role of
default 
defaultPCC
default 
defaultto both the police and local communities. 
default&#xa0;
default5. With this in mind, the NFRN is working towards its aim of meeting all 
defaultPCCs
default over the course of the coming year.
default&#xa0;
default6. NFRN engage
defaultment with PC
defaultCs has already started. We recently wrote a letter to all PCCs regar
defaultding our concerns about shoplifting and the impact it ha
defaults on our members
default’ businesses
